Class AbstractAsyncDataWriter<D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractExecutionThreadService
      • gobblin.async.AsyncDataDispatcher<BufferedRecord<D>>
        • gobblin.writer.AbstractAsyncDataWriter<D>
  • Type Parameters:
    D - type of record
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Service, AsyncDataWriter<D>, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    @ThreadSafe
public abstract class AbstractAsyncDataWriter<D>
extends AsyncDataDispatcher<BufferedRecord<D>>
implements AsyncDataWriter<D>
    Base class to write data asynchronously. It is an AsyncDataDispatcher on BufferedRecord, which wraps a record and its callback.
